# Theme Conventions

Theme-level styles use LESS (not Tailwind — Tailwind is only for React components).

## Colour Variables

Theme colour variables should use a consistent prefix (e.g. `@theme__color__*` for primary, secondary, tertiary, and variants) — always use these instead of hardcoding hex values.

## Custom Mixins

Custom mixins should live in dedicated mixin files within the theme's LESS source directory. Before writing new styles, search the theme's mixin files to see if a reusable mixin already exists.

## File Organisation

- Responsive styles go in dedicated `_media-query-*.less` files (mobile, desktop-medium, desktop-large), not inline in component LESS
- Module-specific overrides use `_extend.less` in the module's directory under the theme (e.g. `Magento_Catalog/web/css/source/_extend.less`)
